line_1: THE eve descends with radiant streaks,
line_2: While western tinges flush the cheeks,

line_1: Of pure resplendent light, in silver streaks
line_2: The fanning west-wind breathes upon our cheeks

line_1: Your brow is crossed with many streaks;
line_2: How wan and hollow are your cheeks,

line_1: Down pensive lean'd her Head; no ruddy Streaks
line_2: Mixt with the languid Paleness of her Cheeks.
